# Python quality

- Run `ruff check` and `ruff format --check` before claiming tests pass.
- Prefer idempotent scripts under `scripts/dev/`.
- Tests must run GPU-free where possible; mark GPU-only scripts clearly.
- No UTF-16 on shell scripts; LF only (see `.gitattributes`).
- Do not commit secrets, PATs, or `.env` files.